&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity for a dynamic and enthusiastic individual to apply for this role within the Bolton Directorate. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This role will provide support to a busy clinical team. The post holder will carry out day to day administrative duties within a busy office environment, as well as providing relevant managers with vital information relating to DQ targets, ensuring accurate, up to date recording of patient information on both Health and Social Care systems, for staff across a range of disciplines. The post holder will work closely as part of a team, sharing knowledge and information ensuring deadlines are met.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is currently full time and may require the post holder to travel to other sites within the Bolton directorate as and when required.&lt;/p&gt;
